gui

Class OfferRequestRidePanel

  • java.lang.Object
    • gui.DefaultView
      • gui.OfferRequestRidePanel

  • final class OfferRequestRidePanel
extends DefaultView
    This class creates the offer/request Pane and the components that make up the Pane. The calling class is responsible for adding the Pane of this class to its view to change the scene so that this view can be interacted with.
    Author:
    Brandon Bonebrake

      • OfferRequestRidePanel

        OfferRequestRidePanel(javafx.stage.Stage stage,
                      javafx.scene.Scene splash,
                      int width,
                      int height,
                      java.lang.String title)
        Creates the Offer/Request Pane that will allow students to create ride offers/requests.
        Parameters:
        stage - Main container that all scenes are a part of
        splash - Previous scene that will can be set back to
        width - Width of the view
        height - Height of the view
        title - Whether it is a ride offer or request
